endd Settings API.</p>\n<p>The latest version fixes a inconsistency when a key has been activated but no return response was generated and the setting was updated, or the key is active but re-saved and showing as deactivated. It also adds a new de-activate checkbox to remove your site from the license to allow activation on another site (if you have a single site license). <em>Note</em> auto-updates will only work on sites currently active.</p>\n<div id="attachment_7752" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 886px"><img src="http://cdn.extendd.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Extendd-Settings-API-â¹-The-Dolorosa-â-WordPress-2013-03-29-14-23-45.png" alt="Extendd Settings API de-activate" width="876" height="468" class="size-full wp-image-7752" /><p class="wp-caption-text">Extendd Settings API de-activate checkbox</p></div>\n<p>If you had any issues with activation, update to the most recent version and de-activate and re-activate.</p>\n<p>The post <a href="http://extendd.com/news/settings-api-updated-to-version-1-0-15/">Settings API updated to version 1.0.15</a> appeared first on <a href="http://extendd.com">Extendd</a>.</p>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:68:"http://extendd.com/news/settings-api-updated-to-version-1-0-15/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:29:"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/";a:2:{s:9:"thumbnail";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:3:"url";s:132:"http://cdn.extendd.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Extendd-Settings-API-â¹-The-Dolorosa-â-WordPress-2013-03-29-14-23-45-150x80.png";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";