s plugin will allow users who checkout as guests to register for the site at a later date. It checks the purchase email against the signup email and registers the user if the email exists in the EDD database.</p>\n<p>Since I recently allowed guest checkouts on Extendd, I built this plugin for the site to allow previous users the ability to register and gain access to recent orders and support forums.</p>\n<p>The plugin has been released on sale for $10! <a href="http://extendd.com/plugin/edd-guest-registration/" title="EDD Guest Registration">Get it</a> before the price doubles.</p>\n<p><a href="http://extendd.com/plugin/edd-guest-registration/" title="EDD Guest Registration"><img src="http://cdn.extendd.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/edd-guest-registration-featured-1024x682.jpg" alt="edd-guest-registration-featured" width="600" height="399" class="alignnone size-large wp-image-7177" /></a></p>\n<p>The post <a href="http://extendd.com/news/annoncing-guest-registration-for-easy-digital-downloads/">Announcing Guest Registration for Easy Digital Downloads</a> appeared first on <a href="http://extendd.com">Extendd</a>.</p>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:85:"http://extendd.com/news/annoncing-guest-registration-for-easy-digital-downloads/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:29:"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/";a:2:{s:9:"thumbnail";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:3:"url";s:93:"http://cdn.extendd.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/edd-guest-registration-featured-150x100.jpg";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"